description:
When you've got big things to do, you need to be connected to your finances no matter what. We understand that you're busy. So whether it's in a branch or on your phone, we do whatever we can to make your life as easy as possible. With our mobile app, you'll stay wired to your money 24/7 and you'll be able to bank from wherever you are. 

With the First Tech mobile app, you can:

ACCESS YOUR ACCOUNTS ANYTIME, ANYWHERE

* Check account balances
* View transaction history

COMPLETE TRANSACTIONS

* Transfer funds between First Tech accounts
* Make deposits with Mobile e-deposit
* Pay bills on the fly

FIND FIRST TECH

* Search for a nearby branch
* Get hours and contact information

LOCATE ANY ATM IN THE COUNTRY

* Green pins on map mark over 28,000 ATMs, free for all members

Don't confine your finances to the walls of a branch. We want your banking to be as effortless as possible, even after you leave the building. With the First Tech mobile app, you're always connected to your money, no matter where life takes you.
releaseNotes:
Here's what's new with our latest app update! 

• Loan Payments – You now have the ability to make your First Tech loan payments right from the app.
